sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant U as user
    participant CLI
    participant C as controller

    U->>CLI: hyper login
    CLI->>U: prompt username + password
    U->>CLI: credentials
    CLI->>C: POST /api/v1/auth/login
    Note over C: validate credentials and mint bearer token
    C-->>CLI: token + expiry + scopes
    Note over CLI: write credentials file (mode 0600) in XDG config dir
    CLI-->>U: logged in

    Note over CLI,C: subsequent calls attach Authorization Bearer token
    Note over CLI,C: on 401 TokenExpired TTY prompts re-login, non-TTY exits 2
